data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the heart of Burnt Store Lakes! This vibrant residence boasts 3 bedrooms and 3 bathrooms within its spacious 2003 sqft under air. The allure begins with the double front doors, ushering you into a world of comfort and style. Revel in the open and airy ambiance created by high ceilings and abundant natural light, creating a welcoming atmosphere in every room. The heart of this home is undoubtedly the large kitchen and breakfast nook, providing the perfect setting for culinary delights and casual gatherings. The master bedroom is a sanctuary of relaxation, featuring walk-in his and her closets for added convenience. Step outside into your private oasis – a heated pool with a built-in hot tub awaits, surrounded by a newly renovated pool cage that enhances both aesthetics and functionality. Dive in, unwind, and soak up the Florida sunshine in style. But that's not all – a new tile roof completed in January 2024 adds a touch of modern elegance, ensuring durability and peace of mind. The A.C. replacement in 2018 gives comfort year-round, making this home a haven of relaxation.
